<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title><%= title %> — SDLMS</title>
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; background: #0f0f1a; color: #e0e0e0; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; min-height: 100vh; }
    .container { text-align: center; padding: 40px; }
    h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366f1, #a855f7); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    p { color: #9ca3af; font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 24px; }
    a { color: #6366f1; text-decoration: none; border: 1px solid #6366f1; padding: 10px 24px; border-radius: 8px; }
    a:hover { background: #6366f1; color: white; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>SDLMS Admin Panel</h1>
    <p>Backend is running successfully. Use the Next.js frontend for the full experience.</p>
    <a href="/api/health">Check API Health</a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
